         <t:div type="translation">
            <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/DH3IFA2B"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Budge1923Miracles"/><title level="m">One hundred and ten miracles of Our Lady Mary</title><author><forename>Ernest Alfred [Thompson] Wallis</forename><surname>Budge</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>Medici Society</publisher><date>1923</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Philology</note><note type="tag">bm:Budge1923Miracles</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Philology</note><note type="tag">bm:Budge1923Miracles</note><t:citedRange unit="page">xlvi-liv</t:citedRange></t:bibl>
         </t:div>
         <t:div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
            
            <t:note>The following division into paragraphs, as well as all Gǝʿǝz text is, if not otherwise indicated, 
               taken from <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/TBQKRU9S"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:TasfaGiyorgis1956Taammera"/><title level="m">&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;ተአምረ፡ ማርያም። ንባቡ፡ በግዕዝ፡ ትርጓሜው፡ በአማርኛ።&lt;/hi&gt; (Taʾammǝra Māryām: nǝbābu ba-gǝʿz tǝrg&lt;hi rend="sup"&gt;w&lt;/hi&gt;āmew ba-ʾamārǝññā , &lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;'Miracles of Mary: Its reading in Gǝʿǝz and its translation in Amharic’&lt;/hi&gt;)</title><author><name>Tasfā Giyorgis</name></author><pubPlace>ʾAddis ʾAbabā</pubPlace><publisher>Tasfā Gabra Śǝllāse māttamiyā bet</publisher><date>1963</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:TasfaGiyorgis1956Taammera</note></note><note type="tag">bm:TasfaGiyorgis1956Taammera</note><t:citedRange>15-20</t:citedRange></t:bibl>.
            
            </t:note>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="basmala">
               <t:ab>በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አሐዱ፡ አምላክ፡</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="title inscriptio expanded">
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="1">
                  <t:ab>ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ሥርዓት፡ ዘወፅአ፡ እመንበረ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ እመካነ፡ መዓልቃ፡ ዘምስር፡</t:ab>
               </t:div>
            
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="2">
                  <t:ab/>
               </t:div>
            
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="3">
                  <t:ab/>
               </t:div>
            
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="4">
                  <t:ab/>
               </t:div>
            
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="5">
                  <t:ab>ወዜና፡ ነገሮሙሰ፡ ሀሎ፡ ጽሑፈ፡ ውስተ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘከመ፡ ተናገረቶሙ፡ ወዘከመ፡ ገብረት፡ ሎሙ፡ ተአምራተ፡ ወመንክራተ።</t:ab>
               </t:div>
            
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="6">
                  <t:ab/>
               </t:div>
            
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="7">
                  <t:ab/>
               </t:div>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="8">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="9">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="10">
               <t:ab>ወአውገዙ፡ ከመ፡ ኢያብጥሉ፡ አንብቦተ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ በኵሉ፡ እሑድ፡ ሰንበት፡ ወበኵሉ፡ በዓላቲሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="11">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="12">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="13">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="14">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="15">
               <t:ab>አመ፡ ፫፡ ለታኅሣሥ፡ በአታ፡ ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ መቅደስ፡ አመ፡ ፳ወ፩፡ ለዝ፡ ወርኅ፡ ወአመ፡ ፳ወ፪፡ በዘገብረ፡ በዓለ፡ ደቅስዮስ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="16">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="17">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="18">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="19">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="20">
               <t:ab>ወአመ፡ ፳ወ፩፡ ለመጋቢት፡ ወአመ፡ ፳ወ፱፡ በዘፀንሰቶ፡ ለመድኃኒነ፡ በዝ፡ ወርኅ።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="21">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="22">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="23">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="24">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="25">
               <t:ab>ወድንግልሂ፡ ታስተርእዮሙ፡ በዝንቱ፡ ሐሙስ፡ መዋዕል፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ዕርዓት፡ ምስለ፡ መላእክት፡ ወጻድቃን፡ ወሰማዕት፡ ምስሌሃ፡ ወተንባላትሂ፡ ወክርስቲያን፡ ይሬእይዋ፡ ገሀደ፡ ወይገብሩ፡ በዓላ፡ በዐቢይ፡ ፍሥሓ፡ ወበዓቢይ፡ ክብር፡ 
               አመ፡ ፳ወ፩፡ ወአመ፡ ወ፳ወ፪፡ ወአመ፡ ፳ወ፫፡ ምስሌሆም።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="26">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="27">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="28">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="29">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="30">
               <t:ab>አመ፡ ፳ወ፩፡ ቅዳሴ፡ ቤታ።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="31">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="32">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="33">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="34">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="35">
               <t:ab>በእላንቱ፡ በዓላተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ በ፪ኤ፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ። ወበኵሉ፡ እሑድ፡ ሰንበት፡ ዘኢበጽሐ፡ ኀበ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ለሰሚዐ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለድንግል።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="36">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="37">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="38">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="39">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="40">
               <t:ab>ወባሕቱ፡ አንስትሰ፡ ይትገልበባ፡ ርእሶን፡ በከመ፡ ነገረ፡ ጳውሎስ፡ ወይደለዋ፡ ንስተጋቢኦን፡ ሕሊናሆን፡ ለሰሚዐ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="41">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="42">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="43">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="44">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="45">
               <t:ab>ወዘተክህሎ፡ ሰሚዖ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ይንሣእ፡ ቍርባነ፡ በይእቲ፡ ዕለት፡ ለእመ፡ ኢከልኦ፡ ደዌ፡ ወምክንያት፡ እውቅ፡ በከመ፡ ንቤ፡ ቀዳሚ፡ ወዘኢተክህሎ፡ ነሢአ፡ ቍርባን፡ ሰሚዖ፡ ይሑር፡ ውስተ፡ ቤቱ፡ ወይከውኖ፡ ከመ፡ ቍርባን፡
               ለእመ፡ ሰምዐ፡ በአሚን።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="46">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="47">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="48">
               <t:ab/>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="paragraph" n="49">
               <t:ab>ወዘሰ፡ ያክብር፡ በዓላቲሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወይገብር፡ ኵሎ፡ ዘተአኣአኣአ፡ ውስተ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ቡሩክ፡ ይኩን፡ ስሙ፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
         </t:div>
         
         
         
         
         
